sources.description:
Summer 1960. A couple of journalists and reckless husbands, with their wives away on holiday, eye two foreign tourists, visiting Rome for the 1960 Olympic event. The wives' early return ruins their plans, and the return of their wives will force them to stage an unlikely scoop.

Original title:  Le olimpiadi dei mariti (1960) 

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/75gXoOUnBes


Director: Giorgio Bianchi
Writers: Vittorio Metz, Roberto Gianviti, Italo De Tuddo
Stars: Ugo Tognazzi, Delia Scala, Raimondo Vianello, Hélène Chanel
Genre: Colorized, Italian cinema. Comedy
